Package: otuSummary
Type: Package
Title: Summarizing OTU table regarding the composition, abundance and beta diversity of abundant and rare biospheres.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sizhong Yang
Maintainer: sizhong Yang <yanglzu@163.com>
Description: This package summarizes the taxonomic composition, diversity contribution of the rare and abundant community 
             by using the otu table which was generated by qiime or mothur. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: vegan (>= 2.0-7), reshape2 (>= 1.4), fossil (>= 0.3.7), reldist (>= 1.6-6)
License: GPL(>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
